  Enterprise 2.0 Project   (小組作業)
  
   Project 之說明與規定
  Each team must has 5 or 6 members (no exceptions). 
				  No on-campus businesses allowed.
                    Please reach out those in need of technology know-how.
                  Judged by group's effort shown during the project, 
                      final grades might be readjusted to an baseline score.
            
  Project 評分表 PDF, or
               DOC
  Business plan 10%, progress report 30%, achievement 60%.
			
